<plot>A Navajo father takes his son on a spiritual journey through the barren lands of the Southwest. The father thinks he might have heard the command of God to prove his faith. He is tormented as the immensity of the task weighs more and more upon him the closer they get to the place of the sacrifice. Surrounded by the austere majesty of Nature's creations, the father must make the most important decision of his life.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?021551</url></doc>
